Hi Frank nice to hear from you,

Glad to hear your still working on the boxes - same here I don&#39;t do hauntings and such just help my wife work with her dolls, many of whom are disturbed spirits donated to us to calm and help and we do..more than 100 of them at the last count. 

We get a lot from them psychically but as I do all that metaphysical stuff professionally which takes up most of my time, then I was thinking that with a box she wouldnt need to depend on my availibility so much to work with the dolls. 

I was thinking perhaps of making something. Haven&#39;t done any electronice for a few decades but I thought I&#39;d give it a go..
I know most of the principles I was hoping to get some practical advise from the forum.

Cheers 

Steve



